<h1 style="text-align: center;">Instructions of Tasavalta
application for Android </h1>
<div style="text-align: justify;">Welcome
to your stay with
Tasavalta-application! This application could
be described as a hybrid of an electronic book, a web browser and 3D
virtual engine. It&nbsp;serves you stories, knowledge and thoughts
you hardly find anywhere else. The information served by
Tasavalta-application is meant to be taken seriously as a proposal how
to improve living conditions of humankind and to secure the continuity
of life on earth.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
</div>
<h2>Overview:</h2>
<div style="text-align: justify;">Tasavalta is an offline
application: this does not send or receive any
data on web. All data, what Tasavalta uses, is installed to your device
with an application package. Tasavalta won't use any other data than
the original application package delivered. If someone has edited or
changed original files, those files have different checksums and
Tasavalta won't open them.&nbsp;<br>
<br>
Tasavalta for Android has three main views. First is Main menu, where
you open files for CAD- and textview and also manage bookmarks, where
you can save to memory present CAD- and textviews so you can easily be
back to them:<br>
&nbsp;<br>
