<br>
The user interface of Tasavalta is in English, but the contents of
&nbsp;textview are available both in English and in Finnish and a
choice can be made in Main menu button ENGLISH/FINNISH. There are also
two other main views, namely CAD-view on the left and textview on the
right, below:<br>
